1)  Create a new directory for the new version, e.g. Debian/TheLastRipper-x.y.z/
2)  Copy tarball to the created directory
3)  Extract tarball in a subdirectory with the name of the package, e.g. Debian/TheLastRipper-x.y.z/thelastripper-x.y.z/
4)  Copy the /debian/ directory from another source package, update control and changelog
5)  Copy tarball to thelastripper_1.4.0.orig.tar.gz
6)  In terminal cd Debian/TheLastRipper-x.y.z/thelastripper-x.y.z/
7)  In terminal debuild -S	(Source package generated)
9)  Create pbuilder environment: sudo pbuilder create --distribution jaunty --othermirror "deb http://dk.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ jaunty main restricted multiverse universe"
10) In terminal sudo pbuilder build ../*.dsc
11) Result is now in /var/cache/pbuilder/result
